What's new
==========

Version 1.1.0
=============

New Features
------------
- compare_probdist

Fixes
-----

- In :func:`pyclimair.plot_variable_trends`, :func:`pyclimair.compute_and_plot_exceedances` and :func:`pyclimair.plot_periodaverages`, when grouping_stat is 'sum', if all values are NaN it now plots as NaN instead of zero. This fixes wrong trend and averages computations due to unrealistic zeros.

- :func:`pyclimair.categories_evolution` now shows NaN values, fixing unrealistic frequencies

Enhancements
------------
- :func:`pyclimair.categories_evolution` now creates categories' labels automatically, disappearing the "categories_labels" argument.